e to revive the commodities market in Nigeria through the Nigerian Commodity Exchange, NCX, and set it at par with other commodity exchanges in other parts of the world. The restructuring will… January 31, 2019 In "Economic outlook" Mrs Zaheera Baba-Ari, the Managing Director, Nigeria Commodity Exchange (NCX), has solicited for “the right policy initiatives” aimed at boosting the country’s non-oil export earnings. April 20, 2018 In "News" Nigerian Commodity Exchange (NCX) has called for investment in commodity markets as it is being done in many parts of the world. February 21, 2017 In "Business"